1h 32m Intermediate Dec 24, 2015   | Uploaded in Jan 25, 2016 by 2boweb
 
Subject: Photography 
Author: Tim Grey 

In this course, you'll join Tim Grey on a road trip along the rugged coast of Maine, photographing lighthouses, harbors, and other subjects, and learn about the gear and photographic decisions involved along the way. The techniques you'll learn can also be applied to a variety of other locations and photographic situations.
